SRC.SAYU Now the animal is more faster!
SRC.TARG.DEX=(<SRC.TARG.DEX> + (100)) 
REMOVE 
RETURN 1 
ELSE 
SRC.SAYU How stupid I am!! This is only for pack animals! 

